xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:prf="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#">  <rdf:Description ID="MyDeviceProfile">  <!-- ********************************************************************* * Hardware platform ********************************************************************* -->    <prf:component>  <rdf:Description ID="HardwarePlatform">   <rdf:type resource="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#HardwarePlatform"/>    <prf:BluetoothProfile>    <rdf:Bag>     </rdf:Bag>   </prf:BluetoothProfile>  <!--***** Screen *****-->   <prf:ScreenSize>320x320</prf:ScreenSize>    <prf:ScreenSizeChar>38x24</prf:ScreenSizeChar>    <prf:BitsPerPixel>16</prf:BitsPerPixel>    <prf:PixelAspectRatio>1x1</prf:PixelAspectRatio>    <prf:ColorCapable>Yes</prf:ColorCapable>       <prf:ImageCapable>Yes</prf:ImageCapable>    <prf:StandardFontProportional>Yes</prf:StandardFontProportional>    <prf:PointingResolution>Pixel</prf:PointingResolution>    <prf:OutputCharSet>    <rdf:Bag>     <rdf:li>ISO-8859-1</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>US-ASCII</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>UTF-8</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>UTF-16</rdf:li>     </rdf:Bag>   </prf:OutputCharSet>   <!--***** Vendor *****-->   <prf:Vendor>palm</prf:Vendor>    <prf:Model>Treo680</prf:Model>    <prf:CPU>ARM9</prf:CPU>   <!--***** Input *****-->    <prf:InputCharSet>    <rdf:Bag>     <rdf:li>ISO-8859-1</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>US-ASCII</rdf:li>      <rdf:li>UTF-8</rdf:li>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:InputCharSet>      <prf:TextInputCapable>Yes</prf:TextInputCapable>      <prf:Keyboard>Qwerty</prf:Keyboard>    <prf:NumberOfSoftKeys>3</prf:NumberOfSoftKeys>     <!--***** Audio *****-->    <prf:SoundOutputCapable>Yes</prf:SoundOutputCapable>    <prf:VoiceInputCapable>Yes</prf:VoiceInputCapable>       </rdf:Description>  </prf:component>   <!-- ********************************************************************* * Software platform ********************************************************************* -->  <prf:component>  <rdf:Description ID="SoftwarePlatform">   <rdf:type resource="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#SoftwarePlatform"/>   <!--***** Basic *****-->   <prf:AcceptDownloadableSoftware>Yes</prf:AcceptDownloadableSoftware>      <prf:DownloadableSoftwareSupport>    <rdf:Bag>     <rdf:li>application/vnd.palm</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>application/x-pilot</rdf:li>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:DownloadableSoftwareSupport>     <prf:SoftwareNumber>4.5.0</prf:SoftwareNumber>    <prf:OSName>PalmOS</prf:OSName>    <prf:OSVendor>PalmSource</prf:OSVendor>     <prf:OSVersion>5.4</prf:OSVersion>      <!--***** Java *****-->   <prf:JavaEnabled>No</prf:JavaEnabled>     <prf:JavaPlatform>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:JavaPlatform>    <prf:JVMVersion>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:JVMVersion>  <!--***** CCPP accept *****-->                <prf:CcppAccept>                        <rdf:Bag>                                <!-- Markup languages -->                                <rdf:li>text/html</rdf:li>                                <rdf:li>text/vnd.wap.wml</rdf:li>                                <rdf:li>application/vnd.wap.wmlc</rdf:li>                                 <rdf:li>application/xhtml+xml</rdf:li>                                <rdf:li>application/vnd.wap.xhtml+xml</rdf:li>                                <!-- Images -->                                <rdf:li>image/vnd.wap.wbmp</rdf:li>                                <rdf:li>image/jpeg</rdf:li>                                <rdf:li>image/png</rdf:li>                                 <rdf:li>image/gif</rdf:li>                                <!-- Audio / Multimedia  -->                                <rdf:li>audio/midi</rdf:li>                                <!-- Other -->                                <rdf:li>text/x-pcs-gcd</rdf:li>                         </rdf:Bag>                </prf:CcppAccept>       <prf:CcppAccept-Charset>    <rdf:Bag>     <rdf:li>ISO-8859-1</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>US-ASCII</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>UTF-8</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>UTF-16</rdf:li>     </rdf:Bag>   </prf:CcppAccept-Charset>     <prf:CcppAccept-Language>    <rdf:Seq>     <rdf:li>en</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>fr</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>de</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>it</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>es</rdf:li>    </rdf:Seq>   </prf:CcppAccept-Language>     <prf:CcppAccept-Encoding>     <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:CcppAccept-Encoding>    <!--***** Input Encoders *****-->   <prf:AudioInputEncoder>     <rdf:Bag>     </rdf:Bag>   </prf:AudioInputEncoder>    <prf:VideoInputEncoder>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:VideoInputEncoder>   </rdf:Description> </prf:component>   <!-- ********************************************************************* * Network Characteristics ********************************************************************* -->  <prf:component>  <rdf:Description ID="NetworkCharacteristics">   <rdf:type resource="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#NetworkCharacteristics"/>    <prf:SecuritySupport>    <rdf:Bag>      <rdf:li>SSL-3.0</rdf:li>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:SecuritySupport>     <prf:SupportedBearers>    <rdf:Bag>     <rdf:li>IPv4</rdf:li>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:SupportedBearers>   </rdf:Description> </prf:component>   <!-- ********************************************************************* * Browser Capabilities ********************************************************************* -->  <prf:component>  <rdf:Description ID="BrowserUA">   <rdf:type resource="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#BrowserUA"/>   <!--***** Browser Name *****-->   <prf:BrowserName>Blazer Web Browser</prf:BrowserName>     <prf:BrowserVersion>4.5</prf:BrowserVersion>    <!--***** Capabilities *****-->   <prf:FramesCapable>Yes</prf:FramesCapable>     <prf:TablesCapable>Yes</prf:TablesCapable>     <prf:PreferenceForFrames>No</prf:PreferenceForFrames>     <prf:DownloadableBrowserApps>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:DownloadableBrowserApps>     <prf:JavaAppletEnabled>No</prf:JavaAppletEnabled>      <prf:JavaScriptEnabled>Yes</prf:JavaScriptEnabled>    <prf:JavaScriptVersion>1.4</prf:JavaScriptVersion>      <prf:HtmlVersion>4.01</prf:HtmlVersion>     <prf:XhtmlVersion>XHTML-Basic/1.0</prf:XhtmlVersion>     <prf:XhtmlModules>     <rdf:Bag>     </rdf:Bag>   </prf:XhtmlModules>     </rdf:Description> </prf:component>   <!-- ********************************************************************* * WAP Support ********************************************************************* -->  <prf:component>  <rdf:Description ID="WapCharacteristics">    <rdf:type resource="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#WapCharacteristics"/>     <prf:WapVersion>2.0</prf:WapVersion>    <prf:WmlVersion>    <rdf:Bag>     <rdf:li>1.1</rdf:li>      <rdf:li>1.2</rdf:li>     <rdf:li>1.3</rdf:li>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:WmlVersion>    <prf:WmlDeckSize>4096</prf:WmlDeckSize>   </rdf:Description> </prf:component>   <!-- ********************************************************************* * WAP Push Support ********************************************************************* -->  <prf:component>  <rdf:Description ID="PushCharacteristics">   <rdf:type resource="http://www.wapforum.org/profiles/UAPROF/ccppschema-20020710#PushCharacteristics"/>      <prf:Push-Accept>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:Push-Accept>    <prf:Push-Accept-Encoding>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:Push-Accept-Encoding>    <prf:Push-Accept-AppID>    <rdf:Bag>    </rdf:Bag>   </prf:Push-Accept-AppID>    <!--<prf:Push-MsgSize></prf:Push-MsgSize>-->   </rdf:Description> </prf:component>  </rdf:Description> </RDF>
